==============
Known problems
==============

* ``dumpdata`` management command will not output the Z coordinates when
  present. Chaining dumpdata and loaddata will therefore not work.
* ``MIN_SNAP_ZOOM`` not taken into account.
* If map view is to wide, no background layer is displayed (c.f. WMS Ã©crins)
* No orthophoto
* Existing interventions cannot be edited
* CSS Fluid rows ignore offset (cf. future bootstrap 2.1.0)

